that's still okay.

23:35.998 --> 23:39.585
Elephant, rhino, monkey.

23:39.585 --> 23:42.880
Bad monkey.

23:42.880 --> 23:44.715
Where do they go?

23:44.715 --> 23:47.885
- They just fall to the bottom.
- What's at the bottom?

23:47.885 --> 23:49.011
Could be anything.

23:49.011 --> 23:51.889
Could be some metal spikes

23:51.889 --> 23:53.933
or trampolines,

23:53.933 --> 23:57.854
or, um, anything.

23:57.854 --> 24:02.441
What do you want it
to be, Craig?

24:02.441 --> 24:06.154
What do you want to find
when you stop falling?

24:08.239 --> 24:10.825
I want to play.
When is it ready?

24:10.825 --> 24:12.827
Um, I...

24:12.827 --> 24:16.122
Maybe we should talk to
Elaine first.

24:16.122 --> 24:19.959
- Elaine?
- She's your creative liaison.

24:19.959 --> 24:23.254
This is sort of what she does,
so that you and I

24:23.254 --> 24:25.423
- don't have to do this.
- Of course. Elaine.

24:25.423 --> 24:26.799
Between the two of us,

24:26.799 --> 24:29.510
I was beginning to wonder
what she does around here.

24:29.510 --> 24:31.512
Good work.

24:31.512 --> 24:33.055
Thanks, boss.

25:13.012 --> 25:14.430
He wants to make it.

25:14.430 --> 25:15.973
What?

25:15.973 --> 25:19.018
In two years, Sang never took
a pitch I gave him.

25:19.018 --> 25:21.562
Patoff shows up and
within a couple of days...

25:21.562 --> 25:22.897
He killed Mama Sang!

25:22.897 --> 25:24.941
Wait. What?

25:24.941 --> 25:28.778
I don't know where she is.
Dana can't trace her. I...

25:28.778 --> 25:30.154
Should I call the police?

25:30.154 --> 25:31.906
No. And what? And say what?

25:31.906 --> 25:34.492
That we lost a tourist?
I mean, come on.

25:34.492 --> 25:37.787
Maybe she just needs a little
time to, you know, to grieve.

25:41.749 --> 25:42.833
Goodnight, Craig.

25:42.833 --> 25:45.336
Wait, wait, wait, wait. What?

25:45.336 --> 25:47.004
What? Are you pissed at me?

25:47.004 --> 25:49.799
I'm too tired to be pissed
with you.

25:49.799 --> 25:51.968
I ache.
I've had three hours of sleep.

25:51.968 --> 25:54.971
All I've had to eat is
a hot tea and churros.

25:54.971 --> 25:56.639
I can't see straight, and now,

25:56.639 --> 25:59.350
I have to drive 40 minutes out
to the Valley!

25:59.350 --> 26:01.269
Did you hear they shut the 101?

26:01.269 --> 26:03.020
Oh, fuck my fucking life!

26:04.355 --> 26:06.774
Yeah.
It's crawling over the canyon.

26:06.774 --> 26:08.442
My carriage approaches.
Are you okay?

26:08.442 --> 26:10.778
Always.

26:10.778 --> 26:12.697
Okay. Well, try
and get some sleep,

26:12.697 --> 26:14.991
'cause we got work tomorrow.

26:14.991 --> 26:16.826
- Okay.
- Bye.

